726011f-a.title: Queens: 221st Street - 41st Avenue
726011f-a.text:
221st Street, east side, south of 41st Avenue, near
the Long Jsland Railroad tracks. The mansion and surround-
ing property was owned by Hannah F. Lawrence in 1909 and by
M. Mickle in 1891.
P. L. Sperr  April 12, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS
